page.title: 06FLORA & FAUNA IN BACK
page.content:
{ HABITATS {INTER-TIDAL ZONE & COASTAL GRASSLAND In this habitat are found:Marine Invertebrates,Oystercatchers,Redshank, Ringed Plover,Turnstone,Terns,variety of gulls,Guillemots,Razorbills & a variety of flowers & grasses. {MOORLAND In this habitat are found:Peewits, Golden Plovers, Dunlins. There are also mink & otters found here, as well as typical heathland vegetation, heathers, mosses etc. {RARE ANIMALS} Rare animals found in this area have included a sea eagle, several corncrakes and a snowy owl.
